### Assets Exception

This license applies **only to the source code** of this project.

All game assets — including but not limited to **sprites, images, textures, audio (music, sound effects), fonts** — are **not covered** by the MIT license.

- These assets **may not** be reused, redistributed, or modified without explicit permission.
- Some assets were created by the project author.
- Other assets were obtained from third-party creators under specific licenses and terms of use.
- All third-party assets are properly credited in the **Credits** section of the game as required by their authors.

If you wish to use any of the included assets, you must contact the respective asset authors for permission.
